    <p>Building a complex editorial workflow in Drupal can be daunting. Although individual pieces of content can be published and unpublished, multi-step processes are often a Do-It-Yourself affair, built out of numerous smaller modules. The <a href="https://drupal.org/project/workbench_moderation">Workbench Moderation</a> module provides a turnkey alternative, combining a standard workflow with just enough customization for site specific tailoring.</p>
